data.description: This spacious home nestled on a generous 0.8-acre corner lot, boasting not one, but two primary suites, and conveniently situated near the Atlanta Beltline Trail – what more could you ask for. Discover the epitome of tranquility, privacy and comfort within the serene ambiance of this residence and its peaceful surroundings all while still in the city of Atlanta.  Featuring a total of 4 bedrooms and 3 baths, this home offers ample space for all, complemented by a double carport and meticulously maintained front yard, alongside a sprawling private backyard retreat. The heart of the home lies in its well-appointed kitchen, showcasing charcoal stainless-steel appliances, quartz countertops, an island, and a captivating statement backsplash, perfect for both entertaining and private cooking/living enjoyment.  Throughout, gleaming hardwood floors provide both durability and a welcoming warmth. If you enjoy outside living, this residence delivers with a front porch, back deck, back patio, and a spacious back/side yard with potential for a pool, promising endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation.  Conveniently located amenities abound, with parks, golf courses, trails, restaurants, breweries, and more all within a few miles' reach. Easy access to Hartfield Jackson Airport, Downtown Atlanta, Mercedes Benz Stadium, and major thoroughfares such as I-75/85 and I-20 further enhance the appeal of this exceptional property.
